{"tid":2370287,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[In朱西WeTrust]中國企業洩2億社交用戶資料Facebook Instagram LinkedIn有份","createTime":"2021-01-18T02:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T08:35:29.000Z","uid":2638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"148cffdd3350896306204bf89112dd170b9f92c2","tid":2370287,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:26:26.000Z","msg":"[In 朱西 We Trust]中國企業洩 2 億社交用戶資料  Facebook、Instagram、LinkedIn 有份<br />\n<br />\n最近大家都相當關注社交媒體以及通訊軟件的安全及私隱度，惟近日又有大型數據外洩風波。據安全研究機構報告指，中國營銷企業「笨鳥社交」因錯誤配置數據庫，意外曝出 408GB 私隱數據，當中受影響的平台包括 Facebook、Instagram 及 LinkedIn，外洩帳戶多達 2.14 億個。<br />\n<br />\n外洩資料庫內含逾 408GB 數據紀錄，當中有 2.14 億個社交平台個人檔案，包括逾 1.3 億 Facebook 用戶、逾 6,600 萬 LinkedIn用戶、以及逾 1,000 萬名Instagram 用戶。據指，外洩資料包括用戶電話號碼、相片、具體位置、公司名稱、營業利潤率等。"},{"pid":"5590f014b007b260659d940cef4802d0a84f547f","tid":2370287,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:26:42.000Z","msg":"經追查後發現，資料庫由中國一家名為「笨鳥社交」（Socialarks）的初創營銷企業擁有，該企主要協助內地外貿企業解決品牌建設、市場營銷、社交客戶管理等問題。 <strong>Safety Detectives 估計「笨鳥社交」錯誤配置數據庫才會令私隱數據曝光，但表示不確定「笨鳥社交」是如何取得如此龐大、活躍且詳盡的用戶資訊。<br />\n<br />\n笨鳥社交至今未有作出任何回應，僅在得到消息當日將資料庫上鎖。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Safety Detectives"},{"pid":"10c0f0fc5337cda7277ef3a718e0342ba932ab0c","tid":2370287,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb18018372ecbe3d0dbe24d212d2b055e042b835","tid":2370287,"uid":281306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bznCyqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbznCyqJ.jpg&h=63b682e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iEo98Y4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiEo98Y4.jpg&h=7a24088f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fb4b6e09e23e04a2c944493793565b83f02863d","tid":2370287,"uid":17103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">但表示不確定「笨鳥社交」是如何取得如此龐大、活躍且詳盡的用戶資訊。</span><br />\n買咪有囉傻閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 豬閪百格"},{"pid":"86fd2f1d2a3f68fc0e3a760e3eaefdcf00ff877f","tid":2370287,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}